{"type": "article", "id": 25600, "title": "橄榄油包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-18T07:08:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 57, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130828mA9LvauUYTrPI7zl.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这瓶橄榄油包装可以从外形上看到橄榄的特征，或者可以看做是一滴油。瓶口的盖子微有倾斜，透过玻璃瓶能衬出里面青绿色，强调了天然的概念。关于橄榄油的信息集中在中间的水滴一样的黑色卡纸上，很简洁。在外面的包装时则恰好将卡纸部分露出来，可以简练而巧妙地表现出信息。设计者来自莫斯科，它目前还是一个概念。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130826m37roD4pyU0Ps8FN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 281px; width: 375px; left: 504px; top: 787px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021308265jlfZ8W7xBOK06e3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130827D34r2pZV61lutcNU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130828Nj9A6uWDU8wTEHOX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}